{"tid":2139634,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"振英評匯豐：這是傲慢。這是偏見。","createTime":"2020-08-04T12:04:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T12:46:38.000Z","uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbcbe960b7f2916f969181436e922fb4977a947","tid":2139634,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"香港賺400億 = 大陸有頂尖人才？？？<br />\n<br />\n傲慢與偏見。滙控上半年在歐洲、中東及北非市場虧損，在香港則賺近400億。滙豐以為在香港呼風喚雨，在西方國家的市場就可以大展身手，這是傲慢。滙豐的頂層沒有中國人，這是偏見。我是滙豐，未來十年，先做好交棒計劃，用人唯才，不能唯膚色，香港和中國大陸有的是銀行界的頂尖人才。<br />\n<br />\nSource：振英FB"},{"pid":"6f6c3b09e3fd2c4fe35220e8ba7751b40f584381","tid":2139634,"uid":47462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"皮蛋黃都唔叫高層？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca21f7c4fdb3b12c6f414c2c239ceb838a5cadd4","tid":2139634,"uid":241504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"咁老實講匯豐仲渣過二線內銀"},{"pid":"d0d9e48acbd5380ad413ab392e6a1a7a2b2fd2ed","tid":2139634,"uid":58287,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ffbcbe960b7f2916f969181436e922fb4977a947","tid":2139634,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"香港賺400億 = 大陸有頂尖人才？？？<br />\n<br />\n傲慢與偏見。滙控上半年在歐洲、中東及北非市場虧損，在香港則賺近400億。滙豐以為在香港呼風喚雨，在西方國家的市場就可以大展身手，這是傲慢。滙豐的頂層沒有中國人，這是偏見。我是滙豐，未來十年，先做好交棒計劃，用人唯才，不能唯膚色，香港和中國大陸有的是銀行界的頂尖人才。<br />\n<br />\nSource：振英FB"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:20:48.000Z","msg":"想做低個價，方便白武士入場。<br />\n連登仔一齊幫手喇。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f18aa6853d2393e886513e13a5eba8d317d7edf","tid":2139634,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid